  "closeout_statement": "LGRC9V3 supports default-off native causal pulse-substrate surface lineage transport. Committed topology events can supersede stale causal pulse-substrate surface rows or transport them through explicit complete lineage maps; artifact-only validators replay the packet/surface/topology/lineage/producer chain; producers are blocked from stale pre-topology surface reads and read transported successor rows when available. Existing fixed-topology pulse-substrate, packet-loop, topology, snapshot, telemetry, and GRC9V3 behavior remains compatible. This closes the runtime surface-lineage capability gap for N04, but does not itself emit movement, adaptive-topology, topology-mutating movement, choice, agency, locomotion-like, biological, or identity-acceptance claims."
